This is for the inner most electron.
One electron atom,

00:24:09.300 --> 00:24:13.180
that will conform to the Bohr model.
And, sure enough, look at the

00:24:13.180 --> 00:24:17.060
ratios of these numbers.
These are determined by x-ray

00:24:17.060 --> 00:24:21.300
photoelectron spectroscopy.
And roughly 14 times four is 56,

00:24:21.300 --> 00:24:25.920
so there it is. One to four to nine
